1. Ti *pušiš* previše cigareta dnevno. (You smoke too many cigarettes a day.)
2. Ja ne *pušim*. (I don't smoke.)
3. Da li ti *pušiš* mentol cigarete? (Do you smoke menthol cigarettes?)
4. Oni *puše* nargilu u kafiću. (They are smoking hookah in the cafe.)
5. Moja baka je *pušila* samo tokom Drugog svetskog rata. (My grandma only smoked during World War II.)
6. Ako *pušiš*, trebalo bi da razmisliš o prestanku. (If you smoke, you should consider quitting.)
7. Nisam znao da ti *pušiš* cigare. (I didn't know you smoked cigars.)
8. Ona je *pušila* kada ju je policajac zaustavio. (She was smoking when the police officer stopped her.)
9. Mi *pušimo* vodenu lulu na plaži. (We are smoking a water pipe on the beach.)
10. Kada sam bio mlad, *pušio* sam marihuanu. (When I was young, I used to smoke marijuana.)